To install the libraries enter the following lines on the terminal:
 
  1)Tkinter : pip install tk
  2)Pillow : pip install pillow
  3)Adafruit_DHT : pip install Adafruit_DHT
  4)array : pip install Arrays
  5)matplotlib.pyplot : pip install matplotlib.pyplot
  
  Time Library does not need to be installed externally as the time module comes with Python's standard utility module.
